<li>_utmb</li>
<li>_utmc</li>
<li>_utmz</li>
</ul></td>
<td>
<p>These allow us to track the number of visitors access the website as well as obtaining the sources of these visits. We can use this information to further improve the performance and user experience of our site.</p>
<p>Further information about Googles privacy policy, click <a href="http://www.google.com/intl/en-GB/policies/privacy/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
<p>To opt out of being tracked by Google Analytics across all websites, click <a style="line-height: 1.538em;" href="http://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
</td>
</tr><tr><td>Cookie</td>
